[I] Run any code on any client

[T] Use the tools you know and the languages you love. Compile everything to
[T] WebAssembly. Run it on any OS or embed it into other languages.

[U] https://wasmer.io

[A] A Bytecode Alliance project
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] base/development
[F] CROSS NO-LTO

[L] APL
[V] 7.1.0

[D] c9b505ae9cd426f7c64fec64b0bf91cb8c5d71228df6156fa74edad8 wasmer-7.1.0.tar.gz https://github.com/wasmerio/wasmer/archive/v7.1.0/

var_append makeopt ' ' build-wasmer
makeinstopt= runcargo=0
atstage cross && var_append makeopt ' ' CARGO_TARGET=${arch_target}
atstage cross && hook_add postmake 5 "install target/${arch_target}/*/wasmer $root$bindir"
atstage native && hook_add postmake 5 "install target/*/wasmer $root$bindir"
